<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Catuaí Shopping — Dashboard Executivo</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&family=DM+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/Chart.js/4.4.1/chart.umd.min.js"></script>
<style>
  :root {
    --bg:#0a0d12; --surface:#111620; --surface2:#181e2a; --border:#1f2940;
    --accent:#e8c547; --accent2:#3b82f6; --danger:#ef4444; --ok:#22c55e; --warn:#f97316;
    --text:#e8eaf0; --muted:#6b7a99;
    --font-display:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif; --font-body:'DM Sans',sans-serif; --font-mono:'DM Mono',monospace;
  }
  *{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
  body{background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);font-family:var(--font-body);min-height:100vh}
  .shell{display:flex;min-height:100vh}
  .sidebar{width:220px;min-height:100vh;background:var(--surface);border-right:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;flex-direction:column;position:fixed;top:0;left:0;bottom:0;z-index:100}
  .logo-wrap{padding:28px 20px 20px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
  .logo-title{font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:22px;letter-spacing:2px;color:var(--accent)}
  .logo-sub{font-size:10px;color:var(--muted);letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-top:2px}
  .nav{padding:16px 0;flex:1}
  .nav-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:11px 20px;cursor:pointer;font-size:13px;font-weight:500;color:var(--muted);border-left:3px solid transparent;transition:all .2s;letter-spacing:.3px}
  .nav-item:hover{color:var(--text);background:var(--surface2)}
  .nav-item.active{color:var(--accent);border-left-color:var(--accent);background:rgba(232,197,71,.06)}
  .nav-icon{font-size:15px;width:20px;text-align:center}
  .sidebar-footer{padding:16px 20px;border-top:1px solid var(--border);font-size:10px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.7}
  .main{margin-left:220px;flex:1;padding:32px 36px}
  .page{display:none;animation:fadeIn .3s ease}
  .page.active{display:block}
  @keyframes fadeIn{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(8px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}
  .page-header{display:flex;align-items:flex-end;justify-content:space-between;margin-bottom:28px}
  .page-title{font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:36px;letter-spacing:2px;line-height:1}
  .page-sub{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:4px;letter-spacing:.5px}
  .badge{background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid var(--border);padding:6px 14px;border-radius:20px;font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);font-family:var(--font-mono)}
  .kpi-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:16px;margin-bottom:24px}
  .kpi-card{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;padding:20px;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
  .kpi-card::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:2px;background:var(--accent);opacity:.4}
  .kpi-card.alert::before{background:var(--danger);opacity:1}
  .kpi-card.ok::before{background:var(--ok);opacity:1}
  .kpi-label{font-size:10px;color:var(--muted);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:8px}
  .kpi-value{font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:26px;font-weight:500;line-height:1}
  .kpi-value.red{color:var(--danger)} .kpi-value.green{color:var(--ok)} .kpi-value.yellow{color:var(--accent)}
  .kpi-delta{font-size:11px;margin-top:6px;color:var(--muted)}
  .kpi-delta span{color:var(--ok);font-weight:600} .kpi-delta span.down{color:var(--danger)}
  .charts-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:2fr 1fr;gap:16px;margin-bottom:16px}
  .charts-row-3{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr;gap:16px;margin-bottom:16px}
  .charts-row-2{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:16px;margin-bottom:16px}
  .card{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;padding:20px}
  .card-title{font-size:10px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:16px}
  .card-title strong{color:var(--text);font-size:13px;font-weight:600;display:block;text-transform:none;letter-spacing:0;margin-bottom:2px}
  table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:12px}
  th{text-align:left;padding:8px 12px;font-size:10px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px;color:var(--muted);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
  td{padding:10px 12px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(31,41,64,.6);font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:12px}
  tr:last-child td{border-bottom:none} tr:hover td{background:rgba(255,255,255,.02)}
  .tag{display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:4px;font-size:10px;font-weight:600}
  .tag.danger{background:rgba(239,68,68,.15);color:var(--danger)} .tag.ok{background:rgba(34,197,94,.15);color:var(--ok)} .tag.warn{background:rgba(249,115,22,.15);color:var(--warn)}
  .bar-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;margin-bottom:10px;font-size:12px}
  .bar-label{width:180px;color:var(--text);white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis;font-size:12px}
  .bar-track{flex:1;background:var(--surface2);border-radius:3px;height:8px}
  .bar-fill{height:8px;border-radius:3px;background:var(--accent);transition:width .6s ease}
  .bar-fill.blue{background:var(--accent2)} .bar-fill.dim{background:var(--muted)}
  .bar-val{width:80px;text-align:right;font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:11px;color:var(--muted)}
  .chuva-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(5,1fr);gap:10px}
  .chuva-card{background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:14px;text-align:center}
  .chuva-icon{font-size:22px;margin-bottom:6px}
  .chuva-label{font-size:10px;color:var(--muted);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.5px;margin-bottom:8px}
  .chuva-num{font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:18px;color:var(--text);font-weight:500}
  .chuva-sub{font-size:10px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:4px}
  .alerta-bar{background:rgba(239,68,68,.08);border:1px solid rgba(239,68,68,.3);border-radius:8px;padding:14px 20px;margin-bottom:16px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:16px}
  .alerta-icon{font-size:20px}
  .alerta-text{flex:1;font-size:13px;line-height:1.5}
  .alerta-text strong{color:var(--danger)}
  .alerta-val{font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:22px;color:var(--danger);font-weight:500}
  .estac-kpi-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:16px;margin-bottom:16px}
  ::-webkit-scrollbar{width:4px} ::-webkit-scrollbar-track{background:var(--bg)} ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{background:var(--border);border-radius:2px}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="shell">
<aside class="sidebar">
  <div class="logo-wrap">
    <div class="logo-title">CATUAÍ</div>
    <div class="logo-sub">Shopping Cascavel · BI Executivo</div>
  </div>
  <nav class="nav">
    <div class="nav-item active" onclick="showPage('p1')"><span class="nav-icon">📊</span> Visão Executiva</div>
    <div class="nav-item" onclick="showPage('p2')"><span class="nav-icon">👥</span> Fluxo & Clima</div>
    <div class="nav-item" onclick="showPage('p3')"><span class="nav-icon">🚗</span> Estacionamento</div>
    <div class="nav-item" onclick="showPage('p4')"><span class="nav-icon">⚡</span> Energia & Demanda</div>
  </nav>
  <div class="sidebar-footer">Dados: nov/2024 – fev/2026<br>Fonte: Supabase CSC-OP02<br>Schema: bi</div>
</aside>
<main class="main">

<!-- P1 VISÃO EXECUTIVA -->
<section class="page active" id="p1">
  <div class="page-header">
    <div><div class="page-title">VISÃO EXECUTIVA</div><div class="page-sub">Indicadores consolidados · Mar 2025 – Fev 2026</div></div>
    <div class="badge">Último mês: fev/2026</div>
  </div>
  <div class="kpi-grid">
    <div class="kpi-card"><div class="kpi-label">Visitantes — Fev/2026</div><div class="kpi-value">335.932</div><div class="kpi-delta">Pico: <span>448.461</span> dez/25</div></div>
    <div class="kpi-card alert"><div class="kpi-label">Ultrapassagem Acumulada</div><div class="kpi-value red">R$ 130.445</div><div class="kpi-delta"><span class="down">7 de 12 meses</span> com penalidade</div></div>
    <div class="kpi-card"><div class="kpi-label">Custo Fatura — Fev/2026</div><div class="kpi-value yellow">R$ 353.605</div><div class="kpi-delta">Pico: R$ 389.344 jan/26</div></div>
    <div class="kpi-card ok"><div class="kpi-label">Consumo Água — Jan/2026</div><div class="kpi-value green">7.094 m³</div><div class="kpi-delta">Média: <span>6.240 m³</span>/mês</div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="charts-row">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title"><strong>Visitantes Mensais por Setor</strong>JAC (Jacarezinho) vs Lago</div>
      <canvas id="cVis" height="100"></canvas>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title"><strong>Custo Fatura COPEL</strong>Total × Ultrapassagem (R$)</div>
      <canvas id="cFat" height="160"></canvas>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="charts-row-3">
    <div class="card"><div class="card-title"><strong>Demanda Máxima FP</strong>vs Contrato 2.200 kW</div><canvas id="cDem" height="160"></canvas></div>
    <div class="card"><div class="card-title"><strong>Temperatura Média Mensal</strong>Sensor Schneider (°C)</div><canvas id="cTemp" height="160"></canvas></div>
    <div class="card"><div class="card-title"><strong>Consumo de Água</strong>m³ mensais (jun/2025+)</div><canvas id="cAgua" height="160"></canvas></div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- P2 FLUXO & CLIMA -->
<section class="page" id="p2">
  <div class="page-header">
    <div><div class="page-title">FLUXO & CLIMA</div><div class="page-sub">Entradas por porta · Impacto da chuva · Passarela</div></div>
    <div class="badge">12 câmeras · Mar 2025 – Fev 2026</div>
  </div>
  <div class="charts-row">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title"><strong>Ranking de Entradas por Câmera</strong>Total acumulado do período</div>
      <div id="rankCam"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title"><strong>Distribuição por Setor</strong>JAC · Lago · Passarela</div>
      <div style="max-width:240px;margin:0 auto"><canvas id="cPizza" height="220"></canvas></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="card" style="margin-bottom:16px">
    <div class="card-title"><strong>Impacto da Chuva no Comportamento dos Visitantes</strong>Média diária por categoria de precipitação · dados reais do período</div>
    <div class="chuva-grid">
      <div class="chuva-card"><div class="chuva-icon">☀️</div><div class="chuva-label">Sem Chuva</div><div class="chuva-num">10.832</div><div class="chuva-sub">entradas/dia · 253 dias</div><div class="chuva-sub" style="margin-top:6px">Passarela: 20,2%</div></div>
      <div class="chuva-card"><div class="chuva-icon">🌦️</div><div class="chuva-label">Garoa / Fraca</div><div class="chuva-num">11.691</div><div class="chuva-sub">entradas/dia · 77 dias</div><div class="chuva-sub" style="margin-top:6px">Passarela: 20,0%</div></div>
      <div class="chuva-card" style="border-color:rgba(249,115,22,.35)"><div class="chuva-icon">🌧️</div><div class="chuva-label">Moderada</div><div class="chuva-num" style="color:var(--warn)">10.981</div><div class="chuva-sub">entradas/dia · 22 dias</div><div class="chuva-sub" style="margin-top:6px;color:var(--warn)">Passarela: ↓14,7%</div></div>
      <div class="chuva-card" style="border-color:rgba(249,115,22,.4)"><div class="chuva-icon">⛈️</div><div class="chuva-label">Forte</div><div class="chuva-num" style="color:var(--warn)">12.083</div><div class="chuva-sub">entradas/dia · 12 dias</div><div class="chuva-sub" style="margin-top:6px;color:var(--warn)">Passarela: ↓12,3%</div></div>
      <div class="chuva-card" style="border-color:rgba(239,68,68,.4)"><div class="chuva-icon">🌊</div><div class="chuva-label">Muito Forte</div><div class="chuva-num" style="color:var(--danger)">8.309</div><div class="chuva-sub">entradas/dia · 1 dia</div><div class="chuva-sub" style="margin-top:6px;color:var(--danger)">−23% vs média</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="charts-row-2">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title"><strong>Centro Médico — Acessos Acumulados</strong>4 câmeras dedicadas (CV34/35/38/39)</div>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:16px;margin-bottom:20px">
        <div style="text-align:center"><div style="font-size:10px;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:4px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px">Total Entradas</div><div style="font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:30px;color:var(--accent2)">625.047</div><div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:4px">16% do Lago</div></div>
        <div style="text-align:center"><div style="font-size:10px;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:4px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px">Média Mensal</div><div style="font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:30px;color:var(--accent2)">52.087</div><div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:4px">~1.736/dia</div></div>
      </div>
      <div style="padding-top:16px;border-top:1px solid var(--border)">
        <div style="font-size:10px;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:12px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px">Portas menos utilizadas (período completo)</div>
        <div class="bar-row"><div class="bar-label">Lago Festval</div><div class="bar-track"><div class="bar-fill dim" style="width:3%"></div></div><div class="bar-val">50.769</div></div>
        <div class="bar-row"><div class="bar-label">Lago CM Esq. 39</div><div class="bar-track"><div class="bar-fill dim" style="width:1%"></div></div><div class="bar-val">17.612</div></div>
        <div class="bar-row"><div class="bar-label">Lago CM Dir. 38</div><div class="bar-track"><div class="bar-fill dim" style="width:0.8%"></div></div><div class="bar-val">12.855</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title"><strong>Visitantes Mensais × Chuva Acumulada</strong>JAC (Jacarezinho) + Lago vs chuva mensal mm</div>
      <canvas id="cChuvaFluxo" height="195"></canvas>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- P3 ESTACIONAMENTO -->
<section class="page" id="p3">
  <div class="page-header">
    <div><div class="page-title">ESTACIONAMENTO</div><div class="page-sub">Permanência · Fluxo veicular · Passantes colégio</div></div>
    <div class="badge">Nov 2024 – Fev 2026</div>
  </div>
  <div class="estac-kpi-grid">
    <div class="kpi-card"><div class="kpi-label">Entradas Totais (período)</div><div class="kpi-value">1.633.393</div><div class="kpi-delta">Horário escolar: <span>10,2%</span></div></div>
    <div class="kpi-card alert"><div class="kpi-label">Passantes Estimados — Colégio</div><div class="kpi-value yellow">39.741</div><div class="kpi-delta"><span class="down">23,8%</span> das entradas escolares não ficam</div></div>
    <div class="kpi-card"><div class="kpi-label">Pessoas por Carro (dias secos)</div><div class="kpi-value">3,51</div><div class="kpi-delta">Chuva forte: <span>3,47</span> p/carro</div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="charts-row-2">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title"><strong>Perfil de Permanência</strong>Distribuição por faixa de tempo (acumulado)</div>
      <canvas id="cPerm" height="175"></canvas>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title"><strong>Colégio — Passantes vs Clientes</strong>Horário escolar: delta entradas × saídas</div>
      <div style="padding:12px 0">
        <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;margin-bottom:24px">
          <div style="text-align:center;flex:1"><div style="font-size:10px;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:4px;text-transform:uppercase">Entradas</div><div style="font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:32px;color:var(--accent2)">166.784</div></div>
          <div style="font-size:22px;color:var(--border)">−</div>
          <div style="text-align:center;flex:1"><div style="font-size:10px;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:4px;text-transform:uppercase">Saídas</div><div style="font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:32px;color:var(--ok)">127.043</div></div>
          <div style="font-size:22px;color:var(--border)">=</div>
          <div style="text-align:center;flex:1"><div style="font-size:10px;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:4px;text-transform:uppercase">Passantes</div><div style="font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:32px;color:var(--danger)">39.741</div></div>
        </div>
        <div style="background:var(--surface2);border-radius:6px;padding:12px;font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.7">
          <strong style="color:var(--text)">Como identificamos:</strong> O sistema registra dois horários escolares: <strong style="color:var(--text)">7h</strong> (entrada manhã: 52.171 entradas, 46.862 saídas → delta 5.309) e <strong style="color:var(--text)">12h</strong> (saída almoço: 100.956 entradas, 69.207 saídas → delta 31.749). O colégio fica dentro do shopping, e pais de alunos usam o estacionamento para embarque/desembarque sem consumir no shopping.
        </div>
        <div style="margin-top:16px;background:var(--surface2);border-radius:6px;padding:12px">
          <canvas id="cColegio" height="100"></canvas>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-title"><strong>Fluxo de Entradas por Tipo e Mês</strong>Rotativo · Credenciado · Mensalista</div>
    <canvas id="cTipoVei" height="70"></canvas>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- P4 ENERGIA -->
<section class="page" id="p4">
  <div class="page-header">
    <div><div class="page-title">ENERGIA & DEMANDA</div><div class="page-sub">Demanda FP · Ultrapassagem · QGBTs · Correlação clima</div></div>
    <div class="badge">Abr 2025 – Fev 2026</div>
  </div>
  <div class="alerta-bar">
    <div class="alerta-icon">⚠️</div>
    <div class="alerta-text"><strong>Ultrapassagem sistemática</strong> — 7 de 12 meses acima da tolerância ANEEL (2.310 kW). Causa raiz confirmada: acionamento de chillers adicionais nos fins de semana e alta temporada. Recomendação: elevar contrato FP para <strong>2.600 kW</strong>.</div>
    <div class="alerta-val">R$ 130.445</div>
  </div>
  <div class="kpi-grid">
    <div class="kpi-card alert"><div class="kpi-label">Demanda Máx. Registrada</div><div class="kpi-value red">2.712 kW</div><div class="kpi-delta">nov/2025 — Black Friday</div></div>
    <div class="kpi-card"><div class="kpi-label">Demanda Contratada FP</div><div class="kpi-value">2.200 kW</div><div class="kpi-delta">Tolerância: <span>2.310 kW</span> (+5%)</div></div>
    <div class="kpi-card ok"><div class="kpi-label">Cenário Recomendado</div><div class="kpi-value green">2.600 kW</div><div class="kpi-delta">Economia: <span>R$ 34.500/ano</span></div></div>
    <div class="kpi-card"><div class="kpi-label">Carga Base Noturna 00h–06h</div><div class="kpi-value yellow">343 kW</div><div class="kpi-delta">Potencial: <span>~74 MWh/ano</span></div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="charts-row">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title"><strong>Demanda Máxima Mensal vs Contrato FP</strong>Pontos vermelhos = ultrapassagem da tolerância (2.310 kW)</div>
      <canvas id="cDemFP" height="110"></canvas>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title"><strong>Custo de Ultrapassagem por Mês</strong>Tarifa dobro sobre o excedente (R$)</div>
      <canvas id="cUltra" height="160"></canvas>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="charts-row-2">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title"><strong>Simulação de Cenários — Demanda Contratada FP</strong>Custo total acumulado de 15 faturas</div>
      <table>
        <thead><tr><th>Cenário (kW)</th><th>Base FP</th><th>Ultrapassagem</th><th>Total</th><th>Economia</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>2.200 (atual)</td><td>R$ 467.071</td><td><span class="tag danger">R$ 130.445</span></td><td>R$ 1.620.544</td><td>—</td></tr>
          <tr><td>2.500</td><td>R$ 532.608</td><td><span class="tag warn">R$ 22.968</span></td><td>R$ 1.578.604</td><td style="color:var(--ok)">+ R$ 41.940</td></tr>
